`f5bigip.sys.Provision` provides details bout how to enable "ilx", "asm" "apm" resource on BIG-IP

{{< chooser language "typescript,python,go,csharp" / >}}





{{< example csharp >}}

```csharp
using Pulumi;
using F5BigIP = Pulumi.F5BigIP;

class MyStack : Stack
{
    public MyStack()
    {
        var test_provision = new F5BigIP.Sys.Provision("test-provision", new F5BigIP.Sys.ProvisionArgs
        {
            CpuRatio = 0,
            DiskRatio = 0,
            FullPath = "asm",
            Level = "none",
            MemoryRatio = 0,
            Name = "TEST_ASM_PROVISION_NAME",
        });
    }

}
```

```go

			DiskRatio:   pulumi.Int(0),
			FullPath:    pulumi.String("asm"),
			Level:       pulumi.String("none"),
			MemoryRatio: pulumi.Int(0),
			Name:        pulumi.String("TEST_ASM_PROVISION_NAME"),
		})
		if err != nil {
			return err
		}
		return nil
	})
}
```

        <span class="nx">disk_ratio</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">Optional[int]</span> = None<span class="p">,</span>
